<p>
<h1>Love In Mud</h1>
<p>
Mud is all around us.<br>
In the trees, the shrubs and in the Folly.<br>
Everyone is touched, from the smallest Firefly1<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;to the largest Bison.<br>
It is present on the fields while the Pony chews the cud.<br>
It is seen when the Dwarfs eat their ham<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;but mostly it is present amongst the players ...
 <p>
Whether it be me and Serenety snogging in a corner<BR>
&nbsp;&nbsp;or Azrael getting cosy in his Coracle.<br?
Everyone is getting it on!><br>
Reverence and Drucilla rocking the canoe of love,<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;or Karya and Lexely making another movie.<BR>
Love is everywhere.<br>
But beware.<BR>
Love can end.<br>
Just ask the Bears of Andarath.<BR><p><br clear=all><div align="right">... <a href="issue.fod_IssueId_8">click here</a> to return to the front page.</div>
